{
  "stem": "14190.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And after a long drive, we were-- we were-- we were brought to  a-- I remember picking from time to time-- a gate opened up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And-- and we were-- we were inside a courtyard and in front of a large building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And again, nuns came out and took us fast from that-- from that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then the priest drove away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were taken to-- to a room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And, again, they gave us to-- to eat and drink.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And to-- we were taken to another room where we remained for the-- for the rest of the night.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And early in the morning, the- the older nun-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I'm trying to remember her name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Dear God, early Alzheimer's, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I forget.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGH] The older nun, a Mother Superior, came and-- and took us in the morning, took us to-- to chapel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the-- the chapel, she sat down and told us what will be our agenda, what we are to do and my chores, and where I can go, where can I not go.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even in the convent, there are several buildings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not allowed to venture to other buildings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are not allowed to venture to other floors of the same building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were to be only in designated places every minute of the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Several times during our stay there, we were taken in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Under-- there was-- there were like-- under the convent, there were corridors and rooms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were hidden there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was because Germans came to raid the convent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- they were stealing from the church.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took the organs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took the things that were made out of brass, out of copper.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
